WP Radar Charts

Installation

Usage

Shortcode

The shortcode [radar-chart] can be used one of 2 way. Either set an ID for a Radar Chart you created in the WP Admin, or by passing all the data required to display a radar chart.

Example of using a Radar Chart post ID
Example shortcode: [radar-chart id="1"]
The example above works for a radar chart with post ID 1.

The shortcode requires 4 attributes to define a radar chart.

datapoints: title for each datapoint in the datasets
labels: the label for each dataset 
data: the data for each dataset
background-colors: the background color for each dataset
